1
00:00:06,980 --> 00:00:10,100
♪I love the clarity in your eyes♪

2
00:00:10,740 --> 00:00:13,860
♪Like a shooting star across my world♪

3
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:17,580
♪Repeating the goodbye we never said♪

4
00:00:18,260 --> 00:00:21,540
♪Through sleepless nights♪

5
00:00:21,980 --> 00:00:25,100
♪I miss the way you looked at me♪

6
00:00:25,700 --> 00:00:30,260
♪Like photos freezing that summer bit by bit♪

7
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:35,380
♪By the shore with warm winds, maybe we'll meet again♪

8
00:00:37,380 --> 00:00:41,460
[Fall in Love Again]

9
00:00:41,460 --> 00:00:43,980
[Episode 17]

10
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:51,080
Where are you taking me?

11
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:53,080
Obviously to sell you for cash.

12
00:00:54,440 --> 00:00:55,920
I bet you wouldn't have the heart to do it.

13
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:57,320
Cut it out. I'm driving.

14
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:00,520
Like I'd ever sell you.

15
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:03,120
I just wanted to get you out, and clear your head.

16
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:08,360
You're the best.

17
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:21,440
Say cheese.

18
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:36,040
No, I don't want to.

19
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:38,280
Just do it this way.

20
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:44,280
Stand right here.

21
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:49,840
One, two.

22
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,440
What did you wish for?

23
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:10,440
[Safe travels. Smooth sailing.]

24
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:11,280
Not telling you.

25
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,440
If I say it, it won't come true.

26
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,360
What about you?

27
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:15,640
Not telling you.

28
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:17,280
Same reason. Won't work if I do.

29
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:18,840
Copy me.

30
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:23,920
- He Zheng! - He Zheng!

31
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,800
- He Zheng, don't go! - He Zheng, don't go!

32
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:40,360
♪Each of us chasing an uncertain tomorrow♪

33
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:44,040
♪Whose pen writes down a few lingering lines♪

34
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:48,000
♪Postcards fading with time...♪

35
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:50,720
Finally ditched them.

36
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,760
People can recognize you now.

37
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,080
What can I say.

38
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:58,520
I'm young and famous.

39
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:00,280
That's idol power.

40
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,440
Hey, idol, I'm thirsty.

41
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,160
Wait here a sec.

42
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:07,800
Here.

43
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:09,880
Cheers.

44
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:12,440
♪Like a shooting star across my world♪

45
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:15,520
♪Repeating the goodbye we never said♪

46
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,760
So, idol, how does it feel now?

47
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:19,560
Stop. Never call me that again.

48
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:21,920
If I'd known this was your idea of a break,

49
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:23,560
I'd rather stay home and game.

50
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,080
Sometimes,

51
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,640
the things that trouble you

52
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:29,040
are exactly what others can only dream of.

53
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,680
I grew up in an orphanage.

54
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,640
Back then,

55
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:38,680
I'd see places like Tiananmen Square, the Great Wall,

56
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,840
Jiuzhaigou and Hukou Waterfall on TV.

57
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,360
And I thought to myself,

58
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:45,240
I had to work hard.

59
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,840
Make more money.

60
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:49,560
So I could see the world for myself.

61
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,040
Later, I became an actor.

62
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:55,120
One crew after another.

63
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,840
One set after the next.

64
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,240
Thirty years flew by.

65
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,840
I've been to many places.

66
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,440
But somehow,

67
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,640
I never found where I truly belong.

68
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,320
Your past journeys,

69
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,120
I didn't get to be part of them.

70
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:20,440
But from now on,

71
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,950
I won't miss

72
00:04:21,950 --> 00:04:23,280
any part of your life.

73
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:42,840
If I get tired someday,

74
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:44,240
come back here with me.

75
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:47,720
Okay.

76
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:50,040
Wherever you are, I'll be there.

77
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:51,680
I'll stay with you.

78
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:54,160
Why are you getting all mushy?

79
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,840
Come on, I'll show you something.

80
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:08,440
Hurry up.

81
00:05:10,740 --> 00:05:12,480
[Five Blessings Arrive]

82
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,920
Why bring me here?

83
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,040
What's wrong?

84
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,160
Nothing.

85
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:19,760
I used to live here.

86
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,280
Why didn't you ever tell me?

87
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:28,080
I lived here with my grandpa.

88
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:30,440
After he passed away,

89
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,480
I barely came back.

90
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,520
What about your parents?

91
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:39,120
My mom passed away when I was three.

92
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,360
Not long after that,

93
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:43,040
my dad remarried.

94
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:47,240
I thought I'd have a real family again.

95
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,880
Turned out I didn't belong.

96
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,560
A year later,

97
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:55,440
I was sent back here,

98
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,440
to live with my grandpa.

99
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,280
I stayed for thirteen years,

100
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:00,960
until college.

101
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:04,640
Why didn't you ever tell me this?

102
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,840
A home needs family.

103
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,480
I didn't have one back then.

104
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:14,520
Then why tell me now?

105
00:06:14,840 --> 00:06:15,840
Because to me,

106
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,480
you are my family.

107
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:20,200
Come on.

108
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:21,440
What for?

109
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,760
We're already here.

110
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:23,800
Don't you want to go in?

111
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,480
Maybe not.

112
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,880
What, not welcome?

113
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:28,680
No.

114
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:32,280
It's just...

115
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,920
I sold the house.

116
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,280
Welcome home.

117
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,160
How do you have the key?

118
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,040
Take a guess.

119
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:44,960
He Jiayang.

120
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:46,880
Idiot.

121
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,640
Listen to me.

122
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:52,160
No matter what happens,

123
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:54,720
you are never selling this place.

124
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,040
Got it.

125
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,440
Thanks for arranging the time off.

126
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:16,760
I'm generous like that.

127
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:18,240
This is just the beginning.

128
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:23,160
You're luckier than I am.

129
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:25,240
At least you have someone to remember.

130
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:28,080
I don't even remember my parents' faces.

131
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,920
Nothing between a father and son is unsolvable.

132
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:32,840
Let it go when you can.

133
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,840
At least you won't regret it later.

134
00:07:45,140 --> 00:07:49,820
[Dinner sometime?]

135
00:07:54,300 --> 00:07:56,200
[Stage 1]

136
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,240
Okay,

137
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,080
Yu.

138
00:07:58,960 --> 00:07:59,280
Okay.

139
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,720
Try a different pose. Good.

140
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,520
Looks good.

141
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:03,840
Alright, let's add some light.

142
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:05,880
Makeup, quick touch-up.

143
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:07,440
Okay.

144
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,240
Alright.

145
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:10,840
Nice.

146
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:14,000
Beautiful. That's great, Yu.

147
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,440
Okay.

148
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:19,040
Yeah, don't look at the camera.

149
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:20,680
Looks good.

150
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,360
Mr. Qian.

151
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:24,480
This is our female lead, Lin Yu.

152
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:25,920
What about the others?

153
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,080
All locked in and joining the crew.

154
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:28,840
This time,

155
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:31,280
thanks so much for your support and trust.

156
00:08:32,030 --> 00:08:33,550
Sounds like my money was well spent.

157
00:08:34,150 --> 00:08:34,960
You can rest assured.

158
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,000
We won't let you down.

159
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,000
Good.

160
00:08:39,670 --> 00:08:40,960
Open your arms a bit more.

161
00:08:41,790 --> 00:08:42,960
This works too.

162
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:43,880
Nice.

163
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:57,040
- Come on. - Let's drink.

164
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:57,880
More.

165
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:01,240
Told you.

166
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,840
Stick with Director Qi,

167
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,160
you'll never run out of work.

168
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,480
That's for sure.

169
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:06,760
This time,

170
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,640
we owe Mr. Qian for the opportunity.

171
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:11,960
Hey, Qi.

172
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,640
Just saying,

173
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:17,240
you should be more careful who you get involved with.

174
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:20,960
Run into someone like Chu Jingxi,

175
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:24,160
and any guy ends up paying for it.

176
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,440
Guess I misjudged her,

177
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:28,120
and almost married the wrong person.

178
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:30,960
I get it.

179
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:31,920
Director Qi.

180
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:36,120
Chu Jingxi's looks,

181
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:38,160
can't really be faulted.

182
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:41,640
Most men wouldn't resist.

183
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:45,040
Her figure really isn't bad.

184
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:49,840
Her figure...

185
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,560
it really stands out.

186
00:09:59,940 --> 00:10:00,920
[Lighting Direction]

187
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:01,720
Want a drink?

188
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:04,560
I can tell,

189
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:07,120
you seem in a good mood tonight, Mr. He.

190
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,760
It's a long night.

191
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:09,960
Sleep can wait.

192
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:12,440
Felt like having a drink with you, Ms. Chu.

193
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,240
So?

194
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,520
Good wine.

195
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:29,640
Just missing something to go with it.

196
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:31,520
That's easy.

197
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:32,480
I'll order something.

198
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:43,840
You're what goes with the wine tonight.

199
00:10:58,270 --> 00:11:01,230
♪When clouds sink into the deep sea♪

200
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:04,510
♪Ripples spread♪

201
00:11:05,150 --> 00:11:07,590
♪Traces of a racing heart♪

202
00:11:08,430 --> 00:11:11,070
♪Is it the sky or its reflection♪

203
00:11:11,670 --> 00:11:14,550
♪I can't tell anymore♪

204
00:11:15,590 --> 00:11:18,870
♪Lost in your eyes♪

205
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:24,390
♪As we draw closer♪

206
00:11:25,390 --> 00:11:27,550
♪The space of an embrace♪

207
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:30,750
♪Scatters the dark♪

208
00:11:31,430 --> 00:11:35,030
♪When the wind comes, raise the sails♪

209
00:11:35,510 --> 00:11:37,310
♪And sail on♪

210
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:42,870
♪Miles ahead are no longer a dream...♪

211
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:46,840
Chu home?

212
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:49,560
It's Yang.

213
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:52,720
Doesn't matter who it is.

214
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:55,080
If we stay quiet, she'll leave.

215
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:57,120
No, she has the passcode.

216
00:11:58,840 --> 00:11:59,440
Then what?

217
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:02,160
Quick, go to the bathroom.

218
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:03,840
Hurry.

219
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:07,360
Get in, now.

220
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,640
Chu?

221
00:12:10,540 --> 00:12:12,560
[Delivery]

222
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:13,360
You're home.

223
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,280
Why didn't you open the door?

224
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,680
I'm in the shower.

225
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:18,040
I brought you some late-night food.

226
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:19,640
Thanks.

227
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,440
Who are you drinking with?

228
00:12:28,280 --> 00:12:29,320
Just myself.

229
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:36,840
Then pour two glasses?

230
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,280
You knew I was coming?

231
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:45,760
Well.

232
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:48,080
Go wash up. Let's eat.

233
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,160
Wait.

234
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:52,560
You can wash in the kitchen.

235
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:55,160
Why would I wash there?

236
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:57,320
Can't I use the bathroom?

237
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,920
Your bathroom...

238
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,720
You're not hiding someone, are you?

239
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:19,920
Chu.

240
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:23,240
We've known each other for years.

241
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:25,080
If you were seeing someone,

242
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,560
I'd be the first to know, right?

243
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:35,520
How could I be dating anyone?

244
00:13:36,040 --> 00:13:38,040
I don't have the time or energy.

245
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:42,440
You and Mr. Song are the same.

246
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,520
Always busy with work.

247
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:45,480
No time for dating.

248
00:13:46,040 --> 00:13:47,440
Right?

249
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,040
Mr. Song?

250
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,240
Why are you here?

251
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:59,440
I can explain.

252
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:30,320
♪When clouds sink into the deep sea♪

253
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:33,600
♪Ripples spread♪

254
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:36,680
♪Traces of a racing heart♪

255
00:14:37,520 --> 00:14:40,160
♪Is it the sky or its reflection♪

256
00:14:40,760 --> 00:14:43,640
♪I can't tell anymore♪

257
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:47,960
♪Lost in your eyes♪

258
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:53,480
♪As we draw closer♪

259
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:56,640
♪The space of an embrace♪

260
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:59,840
♪Scatters the dark♪

261
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:04,120
♪When the wind comes, raise the sails♪

262
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:06,400
♪And sail on♪

263
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:11,960
♪Miles ahead are no longer a dream♪

264
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:17,840
♪Where even migratory birds can't reach, you're by my side♪

265
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:23,640
♪Then I can spread my wings and fly with courage♪

266
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:29,400
♪If storms rise, I'll follow your light♪

267
00:15:30,920 --> 00:15:35,240
♪Trusting we'll reach a warm shore♪

268
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:41,000
♪Where even migratory birds can't reach, you're by my side♪

269
00:15:41,800 --> 00:15:47,480
♪I'll break through the haze and run toward what I once longed for♪

270
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:52,520
♪Even if I'm hurt, I won't wander alone♪

271
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:56,920
♪You're where my heart belongs♪

272
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:14,320
♪As we draw closer♪

273
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:17,840
♪The space of an embrace♪

274
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:20,520
♪Scatters the dark♪

275
00:16:21,560 --> 00:16:25,040
♪When the wind comes, raise the sails♪

276
00:16:25,560 --> 00:16:28,080
♪And sail on♪

277
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:32,880
♪Miles ahead are no longer a dream♪

278
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:38,880
♪Where even migratory birds can't reach, you're by my side♪

279
00:16:39,760 --> 00:16:44,600
♪Then I can spread my wings and fly with courage♪

280
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:50,440
♪If storms rise, I'll follow your light♪

281
00:16:51,880 --> 00:16:56,120
♪Trusting we'll reach a warm shore♪

282
00:16:56,960 --> 00:17:01,960
♪Where even migratory birds can't reach, you're by my side♪

283
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:08,400
♪I'll break through the haze and run toward what I once longed for♪

284
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:13,560
♪Even if I'm hurt, I won't wander alone♪

285
00:17:15,040 --> 00:17:17,920
♪You're where my heart belongs♪
